title: Celtics Palooza With Jackie MacMullan | Real Ones
description:
Logan is joined by The Ringer’s Jackie MacMullan to talk about the Celtics' past, present, and future, including the team’s issues holding onto talent, how Jaylen Brown and Jayson Tatum can play together, and her favorite stories about Kevin Garnett, Paul Pierce, and more.
Host: Logan Murdock
Guest: Jackie MacMullan
